{"tid":1829920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[1月19日] 警方中環拘捕4名男子 涉嫌攜帶鎚仔等攻擊性武器","createTime":"2020-01-19T08:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T08:27:00.000Z","uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"209defa52911f384db1570c06461f769e36734b0","tid":1829920,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503613-20200119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503613-20200119.htm&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1D4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=662bf2d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503613-20200119.htm&h=7586695b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503613-20200119.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站表示，在中環拘捕4名男子，涉嫌攜帶鎚仔、士巴拿等攻擊性武器被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，中環遮打花園下午有公眾活動，為公眾安全，在附近一帶進行截查，並在4名男子身上搜獲鎚仔、士巴拿、伸縮棍、噴漆、手套等物品。他們涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器，或藏有工具可作非法用途被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，會繼續在遮打花園一帶加強巡邏及截查工作，確保公眾活動能夠順利及安全地進行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v09wRbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv09wRbf.jpg&h=c703bc8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c70bf68046deebbae89a3ea2096861666f70149","tid":1829920,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"肯定俾人跟，現在收網，一早有目標"},{"pid":"6b04de7bab3bd76ccf2771f99e8152e9fa7c380e","tid":1829920,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c70bf68046deebbae89a3ea2096861666f70149","tid":1829920,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"肯定俾人跟，現在收網，一早有目標"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"唔一定  隨機搜咗好多人"},{"pid":"2efc96ada9d6e4dbee479f8b44c046dfe8a4a006","tid":1829920,"uid":52468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"209defa52911f384db1570c06461f769e36734b0","tid":1829920,"uid"